    "text": [
        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter with regards to the ongoing construction work at the junction of Finch Street. I reside in the area, and at the same time, I represent my community as I am an active part of the Resident Welfare Association.",
        "Even though the repairs are being done to benefit our neighbourhood in the long run, the workers have created havoc on the roads. We live in an extremely quiet suburban colony and our citizens are not used to the level of noise the labour is creating at all times. They are working beyond the permissible hours, and additionally, they are also littering our beautiful surroundings. Many times, they begin work in the wee hours of the morning and thus we are unable to get the integral rest hours.",
        "I would like to request you to look into this matter on an urgent basis. Moreover, we as a society have drafted a set of rules and regulations that we would like to formalise, for any work to be undertaken in our neighbourhood. For instance, we want to limit the number of hours for the work to be undertaken.",
        "I await your prompt service.",
        "Yours faithfully,",
        "Vasundra Banga"
    ],
